name: donkey
description: A Editor for Valve's KeyValue1 Format (VDF)

scripts.postinstall: echo 'Installing app dependencies!' && npm --prefix ./app install ./app && node rebuild.js

commit.message:
Initial commit

Added Core Files
Added support for plain KeyValue files
Added partial support for Dota2 KV

Read README for more information

releases.body:
[Full Changelog](https://github.com/lolleko/donkey/compare/v0.2.0...v0.2.1)

**Fixed bugs:**

- TreeView resetting after tree rebuild. [\#19](https://github.com/lolleko/donkey/issues/19)
- Tooltip Generator abilities not using the correct id [\#18](https://github.com/lolleko/donkey/issues/18)

[Full Changelog](https://github.com/lolleko/donkey/compare/v0.1.2...v0.2.0)

**Implemented enhancements:**
- Theme Dropdown to Menu Bar [#17](https://github.com/lolleko/donkey/issues/17)
- Add "Add Comment menu entry to the editor context" [#16](https://github.com/lolleko/donkey/issues/16)
- Group KeyValue,. ParentKey & Comment Elements. [#15](https://github.com/lolleko/donkey/issues/15)
- Auto updating [#13](https://github.com/lolleko/donkey/issues/13)
- Tooltip Generator [#7](https://github.com/lolleko/donkey/issues/7)
- Packages Menu Entry [#6](https://github.com/lolleko/donkey/issues/6)
- New KVParser & Comment support [#5](https://github.com/lolleko/donkey/issues/5)

**Fixed bugs:**
- MoveUp/Down command or "Add Variable AbilitySpecial" menu entry broiken. [#14](https://github.com/lolleko/donkey/issues/14)

[Full Changelog](https://github.com/lolleko/donkey/compare/v0.1.1...v0.1.2)

**Implemented enhancements:**
- Auto updating for OSX and windows (Experimental)
- Binaries are now signed

[Full Changelog](https://github.com/lolleko/donkey/compare/v0.1.0...v0.1.1)

**Implemented enhancements:**
- Remove source 2 theme until editor is more stable [#12](https://github.com/lolleko/donkey/issues/12)
- New Data Structure for VDF data [#11](https://github.com/lolleko/donkey/issues/11)
- Create file if the path does not exist 'OpenFileValue'. [#8](https://github.com/lolleko/donkey/issues/8)

**Fixed bugs:**
- Unhandled Exception if invalid dota2 project structure is used. [#10](https://github.com/lolleko/donkey/issues/10)
- Move Up/Down, shortcut not firing.  [#9](https://github.com/lolleko/donkey/issues/9)
- Deleting data via the file tree does not save the file [#4](https://github.com/lolleko/donkey/issues/4)
- Elements inserted into a parentkey are at the wrong position. [#3](https://github.com/lolleko/donkey/issues/3)
- Checkboxes not styled correctly [#1](https://github.com/lolleko/donkey/issues/1)
Initial Release see [README](http://github.com/lolleko/donkey) for more information
